Write unit tests for the navigation history hook.

## Details
- File: renderer/src/hooks/useNavigationHistory.test.ts

## Test cases

### Initial state
- history starts empty
- canGoBack is false initially

### navigateToNote
- Adds current note to history when addToHistory=true
- Does not add to history when addToHistory=false
- Does not add null currentNoteId to history
- Calls loadNote with correct ID

### navigateBack
- Pops last item from history
- Calls loadNote with popped ID
- Does nothing when history is empty
- canGoBack updates after pop

### clearHistory
- Empties the history array
- canGoBack becomes false

### canGoBack
- Returns true when history has items
- Returns false when history is empty
- Updates reactively

