- [ ] Does NOT include @person mentions
- [ ] Displays alias text for wiki-links
- [ ] Truncates long URLs to single line
- [ ] Click on wiki-link navigates to note
- [ ] Click on URL opens external browser (noopener)
- [ ] Shows "↗" icon for URLs
- [ ] Empty state shows "No references"
- [ ] Deduplicates repeated references

