## Layout Specifications
| Element | Width | Behavior |
|---------|-------|----------|
| Sidebar | 320px | Collapsible, slides left |
| Main | Flexible | Centered content, max-width |
| Context Panel | 320px | Collapsible, slides right |

## Animation Specifications
```css
.sidebar, .context-panel {
  transition: all 500ms cubic-bezier(0.32, 0.72, 0, 1);
}

/* Closed state - slides out with fade */
.sidebar-closed {
  width: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateX(-40px);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.context-panel-closed {
  width: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateX(40px);
  overflow: hidden;
}
```

## CSS Structure (AppShell.css.ts)
```typescript
import { style } from '@vanilla-extract/css';
import { vars } from '@scribe/design-system';

export const container = style({
  display: 'flex',
  height: '100vh',
  backgroundColor: vars.color.background,
});

export const sidebar = style({
  width: '320px',
  flexShrink: 0,
  transition: \`all \${vars.animation.duration.slower} \${vars.animation.easing.smooth}\`,
  backgroundColor: vars.color.backgroundAlt,
  borderRight: \`1px solid \${vars.color.border}\`,
  overflow: 'hidden',
});

export const sidebarClosed = style({
  width: 0,
  opacity: 0,
  transform: 'translateX(-40px)',
});

export const main = style({
  flex: 1,
  display: 'flex',
  flexDirection: 'column',
  minWidth: 0, // Allow shrinking below content size
  overflow: 'auto',
});

export const contextPanel = style({
  width: '320px',
  flexShrink: 0,
  transition: \`all \${vars.animation.duration.slower} \${vars.animation.easing.smooth}\`,
  backgroundColor: vars.color.backgroundAlt,
  borderLeft: \`1px solid \${vars.color.border}\`,
  overflow: 'hidden',
});

export const contextPanelClosed = style({
  width: 0,
  opacity: 0,
  transform: 'translateX(40px)',
});
