## Implementation Steps
1. Create the directory structure: apps/desktop/renderer/src/layouts/AppShell/
2. Create index.ts to export AppShell component
3. Create AppShell.css.ts with the styles above
4. Create AppShell.tsx component using clsx for conditional class composition
5. Component should use `clsx(styles.sidebar, !sidebarOpen && styles.sidebarClosed)` pattern
6. Update App.tsx to use AppShell, replacing current layout
7. Add state for sidebarOpen/contextPanelOpen (default both true or sidebarOpen=true, contextPanelOpen=false)
8. Preserve the titlebar drag region (-webkit-app-region: drag)

## Integration with App.tsx
```tsx
// App.tsx
const [sidebarOpen, setSidebarOpen] = useState(true);
const [contextPanelOpen, setContextPanelOpen] = useState(false);

return (
  <AppShell
    sidebar={<Sidebar ... />}
    main={<EditorArea ... />}
    contextPanel={<ContextPanel ... />}
    sidebarOpen={sidebarOpen}
    contextPanelOpen={contextPanelOpen}
    onToggleSidebar={() => setSidebarOpen(prev => !prev)}
    onToggleContextPanel={() => setContextPanelOpen(prev => !prev)}
  />
);
